summary: This MOD is texture only. Eyelashes texture with a high resolution. 1K / 2K correspondence.
descriptionHtml:
[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/91199/91199-1525672855-887213489.jpeg[/img]

[b][b][font=Comic Sans MS][color=#f1c232][size=4][b]About[/b][/size][/color][/font][/b][/b]
This MOD is texture only
Eyelashes with a high resolution. 1K / 2K correspondence.

Easy to use!
Just rewrite the eyelashes of the eye texture with image editing software!
Come now, let 's kill him who is anxious about small devil style makeup!﻿

[b][font=Comic Sans MS][color=#f1c232][size=4][b]Requirement[/b][/size][/color][/font][/b]
Image Editer (Photoshop, Gimp ...etc)
You know How to use graphics software.

[b][font=Comic Sans MS][color=#f1c232][size=4][b][size=4]Treatment[/size][/b][/size][/color][/font][/b]
[list=1]
[*]Open eyes that you want to apply eyelash with an editor.
[*]Paste the eyelashes on the alpha channel.
[*]Save as DXT5
[*]OK!
[/list][line]
